
Recipe For Mango Juice !!!

1. Take two mangoes,
wash them properly.

2. Make small slices of that two mangoes,
and then remaining part means that of a seed,throw it or plant if you want.

3. Then put the mangoes slices in  mixer grinder,to 
make the juice of mangoes slices.

4. After grinder,the juice will be thick.So take a small mesh net bag to remove all 
the thickess of that of a juice.

5.Almost the recipe is done,Now we have to give a final touch.

6.Put the juice in a glass,and then poured some ice cubes in it to 
make it little cold.

7. Now your MANGO JUICE is ready.

                                  THANK YOU                  